<h1>Angela's Recipe for the Best Cinnamon Rolls</h1>
<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<h3>For the dough:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>3/4 cup warm milk</li>
    <li>2 1/4 teaspoons yeast</li>
    <li>1/4 cup granulated sugar</li>
    <li>1 eggg plus 1 egg yolk</li>
    <li>1/4 cup butter</li>
    <li>3 cups bread flour</li>
</ul>
<h3>For the filling:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>2/3 cup dark brown sugar</li>
    <li>1 1/2 tablespoons ground cinnamon</li>
    <li>1/4 cup butter</li>
</ul>
<h3>Instructions</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Mix the milk with the yeast,sugar,eggs.</li>
    <li>Melt the butter and add to the misture.</li>
    <li>Add in the flour and mix until combined into a dough.</li>
    <li>Knead the dough for 10 minuites.</li>
    <li>Transfer the dough into a large bowl and cover with plastic wrap.Leave it somewhere to rise for 2 hours.</li>
</ol>
